OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCouncils call for ban on   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdisposable vapes by 2024   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Disposable vapes cause litter problems,
OL,6, are a fire hazard and appeal too       
OL,7, strongly to children, according to     
OL,8, local councils in England and Wales.   
OL,10,FThe Local Government Association has   
OL,11,Fcalled for them to be banned by 2024.  
OL,13,FDisposable ones have surged in         
OL,14,Fpopularity in recent years, driven by  
OL,15,FChinese brands such as Elfbar and Lost 
OL,16,FMary.                                  
OL,18,FBut the UK Vaping Industry Association 
OL,19,Fsays disposables help smokers quit, and
OL,20,Fcan be recycled.                       
